{"tid":1798462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌落廣告","createTime":"2019-12-26T08:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T20:45:01.000Z","uid":231447,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4b83a7ccf026b0fb65d9499dcd26a055546550","tid":1798462,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:30:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%8f%8d%e9%80%81%e4%b8%ad%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e5%aa%92%e9%ab%94%e8%90%bd%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e6%8c%81%e7%ba%8c%e6%80%a7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%258f%258d%25e9%2580%2581%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e7%25a4%25be%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e5%25aa%2592%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2590%25bd%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%2591%258a%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583-%25e6%258c%2581%25e7%25ba%258c%25e6%2580%25a7%2F&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=27155dda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%8f%8d%e9%80%81%e4%b8%ad%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e5%aa%92%e9%ab%94%e8%90%bd%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e6%8c%81%e7%ba%8c%e6%80%a7/</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我哋之前嚟過2次眾籌落廣告 (可以見到我以前嘅 po)<br />\n但係我哋發覺咁樣好唔靈活，每次要 design -&gt; po 上嚟 -&gt; 等錢 -&gt; 落廣告<br />\n所以我哋今次用 ongoing 形式，大家隨時可以捐錢<br />\n我哋 design 好，就攞錢落廣告，再 design，再攞錢落廣告<br />\n<br />\n第一幅相我哋想 po：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBBWOcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBBWOcb.jpg&h=93a2fb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，我哋想收集下大家嘅意見<br />\n例如應該整乜嘢主題嘅廣告<br />\n點樣先至可以最有效幫到場運動等等<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%8f%8d%e9%80%81%e4%b8%ad%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e5%aa%92%e9%ab%94%e8%90%bd%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e6%8c%81%e7%ba%8c%e6%80%a7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%258f%258d%25e9%2580%2581%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e7%25a4%25be%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e5%25aa%2592%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2590%25bd%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%2591%258a%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583-%25e6%2